---
title: Smart Shawarma-Spiced Tofu  with Spinach Salad and Couscous
description: Tofu is seasoned with big flavour maker Shawarma Spice Blend before being pan-fried to juicy perfection in this recipe. Aromatic couscous and zingy garlic sauce ensure you don't sacrifice taste for calorie- and carb-consciousness.
